rows.label: qst101501_msg0001
rows.name:
If I become debris in the Cloud
Sea, I might find peace...

rows.label: qst101501_msg0002
rows.name: The ship I lent hasn't been returned.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0003
rows.name:
The payment for the ship I
sold is still outstanding.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0004
rows.name: The new ship I built got wrecked.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0005
rows.name:
To top it all off, someone
ransacked my shipyard...

rows.label: qst101501_msg0006
rows.name:
I've lost the will to live, mo.
I have no choice but to become
debris in the Cloud Sea, mo.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0007
rows.name:
I'm the one who did all
that to the ships, but
don't worry about it, mo.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0009
rows.name:
Momo? You'll help me jump
into the Cloud Sea, mo?

rows.label: qst101501_msg0010
rows.name:
If I had a new ship, the vitality
to live for its maintenance and
care might be reawakened, mo.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0012
rows.name:
Umon doesn't have any Green
Pollen Orbs anymore, mo.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0013
rows.name: A new Divine Beast won't come, mo.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0014
rows.name:
Tora and friends are going
to find a Divine Beast, mo?

rows.label: qst101501_msg0015
rows.name:
In that case, I'll wait
just a little bit, mo.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0016
rows.name:
To become debris in the
Cloud Sea, I need to make
my body heavier, so...

rows.label: qst101501_msg0017
rows.name:
I'll be adding weight to my
belly at the dining hall in the
Grodd Residential Zone, mo...
